    <string name="abouts1">Welcome to Survey Calculator, your reliable mobile companion for precise, efficient, and fast field calculations. Built natively using Kotlin and modern Android architecture, this application is designed specifically for surveyors, civil engineers, contractors, and real estate professionals who need accurate geometric and geospatial data on the go.</string>
    <string name="abouts2">In land surveying, precision is everything. Traditional field calculation methods can be slow and prone to human error. Our mission is to eliminate the guesswork by providing a robust, offline-capable digital toolkit that simplifies complex mathematical computations, allowing you to focus on getting the job done right.</string>
    <string name="abouts3">We respect your privacy and data security.</string>
    <string name="offline_desc">100% Offline Capability: </string>
    <string name="offtext">All computations happen directly on your device. No internet connection is required, making it perfect for remote field locations.</string>
    <string name="offtext2">Only Basemap require an active internet connection to load background tiles.</string>
    <string name="datacollection">No Data Collection:</string>
    <string name="datacollection2">We do not track, store, or share your geographical data or calculation history.</string>

